OL,3,CCouncil offering grants to local
OL,4,Cgroups wanting to fly flags in town
OL,6,FRotherham Council will give grants to
OL,7,Fhelp local community groups fly
OL,8,Fnational flags on buildings and land
OL,10,FIt says it aims to encourage community
OL,11,Fpride by giving neighbourhood groups a
OL,12,Fway to show visible symbols of
OL,13,Fnational identity and heritage in the
OL,14,Ftown.
OL,16,FIt comes after flags were removed from
OL,17,Fflagpoles across Yorkshire last year
OL,18,Fover fears it stoked division.
