OL,3,CCouncil offering grants to local
OL,4,Cgroups wanting to fly flags in town
OL,6,FThose eligible can claim up to #500
OL,7,Ffor buying and installing a flagpole,
OL,8,Falong with either a Union flag, a St
OL,9,FGeorge's flag, or both.
OL,11,FIt is open to town, parish and
OL,12,Fcommunity councils, as well as
OL,13,Fcommunity groups with a fixed base in
OL,14,Fthe town.
OL,16,FThose applying must also own or lease
OL,17,Fthe building or land and will be
OL,18,Fresponsible for installation, planning
OL,19,Fconsents, safety checks and ongoing
OL,20,Fmaintenance costs.
