OL,4,Cgroups wanting to fly flags in town
OL,6,FThey grant can only be claimed after
OL,7,Finstallation is completed.
OL,9,FLast year, Union and St George's flags
OL,10,Fappeared across the country, sparking
OL,11,Fa debate about national symbols.
OL,13,FSupporters said the flags represented
OL,14,Fpride and not intended to inflame
OL,15,Ftensions, however others said it was
OL,16,Fbeing used to make refugees feel
OL,17,Funwelcome following anti-immigration
OL,18,Fprotests.
